Type: Package
Package: easydb
Title: Easily connect to databases
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sam El-Kamand
Maintainer: Sam El-Kamand <selkamand@gmail.com>
Description: Easily connect to databases (SQLite, MySQL, PostgreSQL). 
    Just provide the database name and the package will ask you questions to help you configure the connection and setup your credentials.
    Once database configuration and connection has been set up once, you won't have to do it ever again.
